# Agent Forge defaults to subscription-authenticated CLIs — no API keys required
# for Claude or Gemini. But the SDK path and OpenAI both need API keys.
#
# Required tooling for CLI path:
#   - Claude: install Claude Code (https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code)
#     and sign in with your Anthropic account.
#   - Gemini: `npm install -g @google/gemini-cli`, then run `gemini` once and
#     sign in with Google.
#
# API keys (for SDK path — fill in only what you use):

# Anthropic API — SDK path for Claude. Optional; Claude CLI preferred.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Google Gemini API — SDK path for Gemini. Set if you don't have gemini CLI.
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy...

# OpenAI API — SDK path for GPT-5 and o-series reasoning models.
# Required for Polymath (Tri-Model) and Triple-Model Braintrust teams.
# Get at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-...
